{"tid":2364544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏蘭特今夏逃離多蒙特！拉奧拿已有行動","createTime":"2021-01-13T05:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T06:55:38.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d904944d79c50da3acc4ba867171b44dc0b6169c","tid":2364544,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"　　夏蘭特（Erling Haland）是當今球壇新一代中，最具名氣的球星，他的未來牽動著頂級豪門的心。如今巴塞在夏蘭特爭奪戰中，佔據了優勢地位。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據《加泰電台》報導，夏蘭特下季將不會留在多蒙特，他的經理人拉奧拿（Mino Raiola）準備將他運作到巴塞，因為這位超級經理人，想要通過這單轉會案，來打好和巴塞之間的關係。<br />\n<br />\n　　夏蘭特如今才20歲，但他已經是球壇最優秀的前鋒之一。看看他今季的數據&mdash;&mdash;15場19球。如此效率，比之巔峰「美C」也不差。<br />\n<br />\n　　目前，有意夏蘭特的球隊很多，包括大巴黎、皇馬、巴塞、曼聯等頂級豪門。接下來，就看各方的運作了。"},{"pid":"ddd058aa5ad11b6eb9bc3fe731f372f005cd835e","tid":2364544,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"下欄凸1.8億都值，仲好用過麥包"},{"pid":"193bc36bc7bb089c86fa22d94efcbcefd8fbaef6","tid":2364544,"uid":158755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddd058aa5ad11b6eb9bc3fe731f372f005cd835e","tid":2364544,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"下欄凸1.8億都值，仲好用過麥包"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:37:39.000Z","msg":"包皮去其他聯賽對中下游唔會有位爆"},{"pid":"f51a1b09727dd1ba2627d6cba58bc098fd1f38d2","tid":2364544,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"又係拉奧拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294327e8e543120d71e3e1ebc45690ae78eeff3e","tid":2364544,"uid":238920,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:39:14.000Z","msg":"準備將他運作到巴塞<br />\n<br />\n垃圾支那文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"